item.title: About
item.description: Developer, dreamer, manga lover. My name is Dogukan KOKCE. I’m 21 years old. I have more than several years of experience in PHP-Laravel(Web App Development) and Java(Android app Development). Currently I am studying at Akdeniz University and also working as an independent consultant for Laravel, and web development. Always interested in to learn something new and create new projects for people and companies.
